{"id": 839, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于健身房你有什么要吐槽的？", "description": "不只是声音。不只是气味。", "record_count": 3803, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016070218361501rMpKOLGhQWNvko.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-28T01:00:19Z", "options": [{"id": 55296, "content": "肥皂常丢?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447378}, {"id": 54273, "content": "不开心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489705}, {"id": 54274, "content": "练瑜伽最怕用到破旧的公用瑜伽垫，散发着幽幽臭味。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494781}, {"id": 54530, "content": "看見又胖又醜的大媽們，跟著長相似小鮮肉的教練打情罵俏，噁心死我了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458051}, {"id": 54275, "content": "哼唧怪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473884}, {"id": 54276, "content": "卧推到一半你摘我个杠铃片是几个意思…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414794}, {"id": 54278, "content": "器械坏了不修咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479417}, {"id": 55047, "content": "啊啊啊啊的在那乱叫 像叫床 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316395}, {"id": 54281, "content": "自信过头浑身肌肉的私教每每出现在你眼前或身边时，就是五味杂陈，最好拔腿就跑的感觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274959}, {"id": 54286, "content": "现在办卡最划算，我们马上就会涨价。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153902}, {"id": 66575, "content": "给了钱却没有服务意识。就最基本的安全考虑来讲，在英国时去的健身房会为每一个顾客第一次健身的时候制定健身计划，并且定期Review。国内的教练就只会给可能购买私教的人安利，不会健身的人在健身房内踌躇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564116}, {"id": 54287, "content": "教练和学员打情骂俏……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429673}, {"id": 56592, "content": "教练帮你瘦身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486219}, {"id": 54289, "content": "办了卡却没去过几次！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290001}, {"id": 54290, "content": "比起健身你更想看隔壁的大胸妹！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290001}, {"id": 54293, "content": "让人受不了的音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357362}, {"id": 54294, "content": "霸着几种器械的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411666}, {"id": 54295, "content": "大爷总把健身房当洗澡房", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494976}, {"id": 54296, "content": "经常莫名其妙地停水，瑜伽垫子好脏，健身房里“人”味儿好重！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493425}, {"id": 54298, "content": "占着器械当座位的啊喂&“我来给你做些指导吧”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494994}, {"id": 54301, "content": "抬头看看其他人的肌肉，我又放弃了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490690}, {"id": 54302, "content": "美女太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268063}, {"id": 55327, "content": "眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490571}, {"id": 54305, "content": "然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495017}, {"id": 54309, "content": "我一个偏瘦女生不到100斤 脂肪含量23%算比较标准，结果肌肉教练那么粗壮 脂肪含量才10%……好变态……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495036}, {"id": 54310, "content": "好吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493466}, {"id": 56362, "content": "........", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4119}, {"id": 57131, "content": "没坚持健身两个月的人，怎么能来这吐槽？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511366}, {"id": 54318, "content": "私教嘴里我一身都是不合格零件，必须配合各种训练。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475835}, {"id": 54319, "content": "总有人健身发出莫名的喊声", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475835}, {"id": 56623, "content": "一定要去那看姑娘吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 54320, "content": "健身器材抓起来永远汗腻腻的，到底有没有人清洁啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475835}, {"id": 54321, "content": "动感单车前面人屁股离你的脸有点近 ......噢买尬~什么味道~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495111}, {"id": 54322, "content": "身材不怎样但就是喜欢去撩女生的中年大叔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490052}, {"id": 54323, "content": "缺少一个良好的运动环境。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55989}, {"id": 54325, "content": "交了月卡却只去了三次的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479072}, {"id": 58934, "content": "器械不行。跑步机太旧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518377}, {"id": 54327, "content": "遗留在各种器械上的酸臭腐朽汗味儿……想想都要吐了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495181}, {"id": 54583, "content": "你说什么？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405037}, {"id": 54328, "content": "实际上跟你聊天的人都只是在关心自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495183}, {"id": 55868, "content": "裸着上半身使用器械，用完还不擦如果上面如果水泼过的汗水", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41653}, {"id": 60479, "content": "一些水平不如你的人在你做完一组动作后马上把重量加大，然后用毫不标准的姿势乱做一通，还颇具优越感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527655}, {"id": 62015, "content": "没命的自拍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533598}, {"id": 54337, "content": "瘦瘦小小不穿制服我都不知道他是教练", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478622}, {"id": 54339, "content": "一直在转让", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495219}, {"id": 54340, "content": "打嗝的味道，想骂人！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477813}, {"id": 54341, "content": "这个图 密集恐惧症啊 能不能不要再做这个调查了？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489126}, {"id": 54343, "content": "坚持之后就成为一种习惯了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495259}, {"id": 54344, "content": "办了卡只去一个星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462213}, {"id": 61257, "content": "当然是气氛，一个人健身就不叫健身房了。既然是健身房，当然人越多越来劲??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519484}]}